overview: Barstow and Stevens are forcing the local printer to print fake silver certificates which they then sell. Treasury Agents Chick Weaver and Throckmorton Snodgrass arrive working under cover. But when Chick's true identity as an Agent is revealed, Barstow sends his henchmen to finish him off.
tagline: MURDERERS UNMASKED!...In a bursting blaze of breakneck battles...and thrill-a-minute triumphs!
title: Stagecoach to Monterey
